Given	I'm logged-in with valid credentials
And I select 'Female' radio button from Page 01 of Pelvic MRI
And I select any Examination radio button from Page 01 of Pelvic MRI
And I go to Page 09 of Pelvic MRI
And I select 'Finding' radio button
And I select 'Urinary bladder wall thickening' from the dropdown menu

When I select 'Characterization II' tab
Then 'Calcification' checkbox is enabled
And 'Exophytic growth' radio button is enabled
And 'Infiltrative growth' radio button is enabled
And 'Bladder wall infiltration through extravesical primary tumour' radio button is enabled
And 'Bladder wall displacement due to extravesical primary tumour' radio button is enabled

And 'Differential diagnosis 1' dropdown menu is enabled
And '> 1 lesion, same entity' checkbox is enabled

When I select 'Calcification' checkbox
Then the checkbox is checked

When I select 'Exophytic growth' radio button
Then radio button is selected

When I select 'Infiltrative growth' radio button
Then 'Muscularis propria' radio button is enabled
And 'Perivesical fat tissue' radio button is enabled
And 'Uterus/Ovary' radio button is enabled
And 'Pelvic wall/Abdominal wall' radio button is enabled

When I select 'Muscularis propria' radio button
Then radio button is selected
When I select 'Perivesical fat tissue' radio button
Then radio button is selected
When I select 'Uterus/Ovary' radio button
Then radio button is selected
When I select 'Pelvic wall/Abdominal wall' radio button
Then radio button is selected

When I select 'Bladder wall infiltration through extravesical primary tumour' radio button
Then radio button is selected
When I select 'Bladder wall displacement due to extravesical primary tumour' radio button
Then radio button is selected

When I select 'Endometriosis' from Differential diagnosis 1' dropdown menu
Then 'Differential diagnosis 2' dropdown menu is enabled

When I select 'Infiltrated by uterus/ovarian carcinoma' from Differential diagnosis 2' dropdown menu
Then 'Subordinate' checkbox is enabled

When I select 'Subordinate' checkbox
Then checkbox is checked

When I select '> 1 lesion, same entity' checkbox
Then checkbox is checked

When I select 'Artifacts' checkbox
Then checkbox is checked
When I select 'Not sufficient bladder filling' checkbox
Then checkbox is checked
When I select 'Inserted bladder catheter' checkbox
Then checkbox is checked
When I select 'Double-j catheter right' checkbox
Then checkbox is checked
When I select 'Double-j catheter left' checkbox
Then checkbox is checked
